{"id":"21065","name":"今日好手氣","rarity":4,"path":"Elation","desc":"「師妹，你確信無疑？」\n「哼，絕無錯漏！」\n「這次的賭注可不只一瓶護手霜哦。」\n「如此簡單的遊戲……豈會有變數？」\n粉髮女孩轉過身，拒絕再受其擾。\n「以茶葉浮沉的跡象來看，師妹你該出那張才是。」\n少女抽籤，反轉出示——\n「呀，我的好手氣來了。」\n「再來再來，這絕對不可能……」\n……\n女孩忘了和師姐玩過多少占卜遊戲，只記得師姐總願意陪她重來。\n後來，女孩想要逃離命定的預言，不顧阻撓，去了羅浮太卜司。\n初到羅浮，她忽然從卜書的夾縫中發現一張精緻的符籤，熟悉的筆跡讓在異鄉的女孩紅了眼眶：\n「誰說命運沒有第二種可能？我的轉運符，送給你囉～」","icon":"icon/light_cone/21065.png","preview":"image/light_cone_preview/21065.png","portrait":"image/light_cone_portrait/21065.png","ranks":{"id":"21065","skill":"抉擇","desc":"使裝備者的暴擊率提高#1[i]%。裝備者施放歡愉技時，歡愉度提高#2[i]%，該效果最多疊加#3[i]次。","params":[[0.12,0.12,2],[0.14,0.14,2],[0.16,0.16,2],[0.18,0.18,2],[0.2,0.2,2]],"properties":[[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.12}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.14}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.16}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.18}],[{"type":"CriticalChanceBase","value":0.2}]]},"promotions":{"id":"21065","values":[{"hp":{"base":43.2,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":24,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":18,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":95.04,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":52.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":39.6,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":164.16,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":91.2,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":68.4,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":233.28,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":129.6,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":97.2,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":302.4,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":168,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":126,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":371.52,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":206.4,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":154.8,"step":2.7}},{"hp":{"base":440.64,"step":6.48},"atk":{"base":244.8,"step":3.6},"def":{"base":183.6,"step":2.7}}],"materials":[[{"id":"2","num":4000},{"id":"116001","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":8000},{"id":"110261","num":3},{"id":"116001","num":10}],[{"id":"2","num":16000},{"id":"110262","num":3},{"id":"116002","num":6}],[{"id":"2","num":40000},{"id":"110262","num":6},{"id":"116002","num":9}],[{"id":"2","num":80000},{"id":"110263","num":4},{"id":"116003","num":5}],[{"id":"2","num":160000},{"id":"110263